datasets.name: dataset_17
queryLines: SELECT `Home Tile`, MEASURE(SUM(`Unique Tile Views`)) AS `Unique Tile Views`, MEASURE(SUM(`Unique Tile Clicks`)) AS `Unique Tile Clicks`, MEASURE(SUM(`Unique Interstitial Views`)) AS `Unique Interstitial Views`, MEASURE(SUM(`Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`)) AS `Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`, MEASURE(SUM(`Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`)) AS `Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`, MEASURE(SUM(`Home Tile Clicked Vs Homepage Displayed`)) AS `% Home Tile Clicked Vs Homepage Displayed`, MEASURE(SUM(`Primary Button Clicked Vs Tile Displayed`)) AS `% Primary Button Clicked Vs Tile Displayed`, MEASURE(SUM(`Secondary Button Clicked Vs Tile Displayed`)) AS `% Secondary Button Clicked Vs Tile Displayed`, MEASURE(SUM(`Primary Button Clicked Vs Interstitial Displayed`)) AS `% Primary Button Clicked Vs Interstitial Displayed`, MEASURE(SUM(`Secondary Button Clicked Vs Interstitial Displayed`)) AS `% Secondary Button Clicked Vs Interstitial Displayed`, MEASURE(SUM(`f_ctr`)) AS `CTR` FROM workspace.default.mv_hpx_events_model_homepage_summary GROUP BY `Home Tile` ORDER BY MEASURE(SUM(`CTR`)) DESC
